    "data": [
        {
            "title": "耿長有任中紀委駐中央港澳辦紀檢組長",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"耿長有任中紀委駐中央港澳辦紀檢組長。中央港澳辦官網\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/29dfcf6842fd0e14e5084e050589bafe/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031017154470620.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">耿長有任中紀委駐中央港澳辦紀檢組長。中央港澳辦官網</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中央港澳辦官網顯示，耿長有已任中央紀委國家監委駐中央港澳工作辦公室紀檢監察組組長。\n\n</p>\n<p>公開資料顯示，耿長有，漢族，研究生，曾任中央宣傳部幹部局局長、中央巡視組副部級巡視專員等職。\n\n</p>\n<p>原任中央紀委國家監委駐中央港澳工作辦公室紀檢監察組組長的是施克輝，已經超過63歲的退休年齡。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057349/即時-中國-耿長有任中紀委駐中央港澳辦紀檢組長",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 17:21:35",
