            "title": "緹外4房大宅2.3億沽 呎價5.18萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"緹外4房大宅2.3億沽 呎價5.18萬\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/91becbc9bd4539207d1c0f1b935f518e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031016522363279.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">緹外4房大宅2.3億沽 呎價5.18萬</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>嘉里建設發展之九龍半山超級豪宅緹外剛以招標方式售出4房大宅，成交價2.3億，呎價約5.18萬，項目本季至今已連沽3伙。\n\n</p>\n<p>緹外剛售出5座3樓A室連傢俬分層大宅，面積4,437方呎，屬4套房另加雙工人房間隔，以2.3億元成交，呎價約51,837元。上述單位成交價包括2個住宅停車位。項目今年以來暫沽3伙，共涉額5.87億。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057343/即時-地產-緹外4房大宅2-3億沽-呎價5-18萬",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-10 16:56:20",
