            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "西甲｜皇馬2:1勝華歷簡奴 末段主守被球迷喝倒采",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"皇馬2:1勝華歷簡奴，末段主守被球迷喝倒采。REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/46e8274a4ba8579d81a52b7af3aaedc4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250310/_2025031016515915565.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">皇馬2:1勝華歷簡奴，末段主守被球迷喝倒采。REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>皇家馬德里周日西甲主場2:1擊敗華歷簡奴，並乘同市宿敵馬德里體育會同日輸波，於聯賽榜皇馬以1分反壓馬體會進佔次席。不過，皇馬於比賽末段退守後防，惹來班拿背主場球迷報以噓聲，皇馬教練安察洛堤為球隊辯護，指比賽末段領先1球唯一的任務是做好防守。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲尼斯奧斯(白衫)起腳射門。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2366353b4ef5f6216145cd4fdbb6bc55/2025-03/2025-03-09T155700Z_2131643054_UP1EL3918AYVT_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-RMA-RAY-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲尼斯奧斯(白衫)起腳射門。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"皇家馬德里(白衫)2:1僅勝華歷簡奴(灰衫)。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1fd256f0620df52abd75cb900e85ddd2/2025-03/2025-03-09T154834Z_1322669987_UP1EL3917WWUK_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-RMA-RAY-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇家馬德里(白衫)2:1僅勝華歷簡奴(灰衫)。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"射手麥巴比(白衫)為皇家馬德里先開紀錄。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/812271fb9728181953a031d1292c00a3/2025-03/2025-03-09T155056Z_2001919770_UP1EL39180UUU_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-RMA-RAY-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        射手麥巴比(白衫)為皇家馬德里先開紀錄。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲尼斯奧斯(左)射成2:0。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7a11ec0a6881f2e8ada3857d3a859a9a/2025-03/2025-03-09T155528Z_529946996_UP1EL39188FVJ_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-RMA-RAY-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲尼斯奧斯(左)射成2:0。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲尼斯奧斯射成2:0。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f6c9f7cc6574510b15d5226fea30665a/2025-03/2025-03-09T155627Z_710029088_UP1EL3918A1VQ_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-RMA-RAY-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲尼斯奧斯射成2:0。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"射手麥巴比(白衫)為皇家馬德里先開紀錄。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a50e15e522a5d53da27b86445f51248e/2025-03/2025-03-09T160233Z_766996203_UP1EL3918K7WT_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-RMA-RAY-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        射手麥巴比(白衫)為皇家馬德里先開紀錄。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"射手麥巴比為皇家馬德里先開紀錄。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/326813dbd54524aff0c137666339609a/2025-03/2025-03-09T174158Z_789785452_UP1EL39181FUY_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-SPAIN-RMA-RAY-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        射手麥巴比為皇家馬德里先開紀錄。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>皇馬半場領先2:1</h2>\n<p>擁有基利安麥巴比、雲尼斯奧斯祖利亞、祖迪比寧咸和洛迪高高斯的銀河艦隊鋒線，甫開賽即展開強攻，14分鐘雲尼斯奧斯接應右路傳中禁區邊起腳射中柱。戰至29分鐘，皇馬終由基利安麥巴比左路突入禁區，再扣入中路施射地波入網打開紀錄。34分鐘輪到雲尼斯奧斯同樣於左路進攻，引球推入禁區避過兩名後衛施射破網，將紀錄改寫成2:0。\n\n</p><h2>VAR判華歷簡奴入球</h2>\n<p>不過，皇馬未能將兩球領先優勢帶回更衣室，華歷簡奴於上半場補時2分鐘由中場柏度戴亞斯禁區頂勁射，皮球中橫楣彈地而出，球證經VAR判斷皮球彈地時已越過白界，華歷簡奴追近至1:2完半場。\n\n</p><h2>安察洛堤指末段防守無錯</h2>\n<p>換邊後，皇馬54分鐘有麥巴比於左路突入禁區起腳，皮球貼左邊門柱出界。75分鐘，輪到中場莫迪歷左路快放傳中，雲尼斯奧斯近柱接應撞射，皮球又於右門柱邊出界。久攻不下皇馬反被華歷簡奴進攻，於末段主守遭到主場球迷喝倒采，最後仍成功保住2:1勝局。教練安察洛堤賽後為球隊辯護：「當比賽踢到70分鐘領先2:1時，球隊就要做好一件事情，那就旦是防守，避免出現任何問題。我們最後守得很好，避免問題產生，我明白球迷不喜歡我們末段的演出，但要知道有多支出戰歐聯球隊今周輸波。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057342/即時-體育-西甲-皇馬2-1勝華歷簡奴-末段主守被球迷喝倒采",
